Scheduling a ustream for recording:

./schedule.sh <start time> <stop time> <ustream url> <output.flv>

Example:

./schedule.sh "20:23 today" "20:26 today" http://www.ustream.tv/ELECTRIFIED output.flv

Requirements (must be enabled for scheduling to work):

Enable 'at' scheduling:

sudo launchctl load -w /System/Library/LaunchDaemons/com.apple.atrun.plist

Disable 'at' scheduling:

sudo launchctl unload -w /System/Library/LaunchDaemons/com.apple.atrun.plist
